<p id="fs-idp167647504">To summarize: at equilibrium [H<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3</sub>] = 0.033 <em data-effect="italics">M</em>; <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><msub><mrow><mtext>H</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><msup><mtext>O</mtext><mtext>+</mtext></msup><mo stretchy="false">]</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><msub><mrow><mtext>H</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><msup><mtext>O</mtext><mtext>+</mtext></msup><mo stretchy="false">]</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> = 1.2 <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo>&#215;</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo>&#215;</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> 10<sup>&#8722;4</sup>; <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><msub><mrow><mtext>HCO</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><msup><mrow/><mtext>&#8722;</mtext></msup><mo stretchy="false">]</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>1.2</mn><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo>&#215;</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow><mn>&#8722;4</mn></mrow></msup><mspace width="0.2em"/><mi>M</mi><mo>;</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><msub><mrow><mtext>HCO</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><msup><mrow/><mtext>&#8722;</mtext></msup><mo stretchy="false">]</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>1.2</mn><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo>&#215;</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow><mn>&#8722;4</mn></mrow></msup><mspace width="0.2em"/><mi>M</mi><mo>;</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><msub><mrow><mtext>CO</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><msup><m