<p id="fs-idm17589920">Calculate the concentration of each species present in a 0.010-<em data-effect="italics">M</em> solution of phthalic acid, C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>(CO<sub>2</sub>H)<sub>2</sub>.<span data-type="newline"><br/></span>
