</div>
<div data-type="solution" id="fs-idm62337840">
<p id="fs-idp126090960">[C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>(CO<sub>2</sub>H)<sub>2</sub>] 7.2 <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo>&#215;</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo>&#215;</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> 10<sup>&#8722;3</sup> <em data-effect="italics">M</em>, [C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>(CO<sub>2</sub>H)(CO<sub>2</sub>)<sup>&#8722;</sup>] = [H<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup>] 2.8 <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo>&#215;</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo>&#215;</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> 10<sup>&#8722;3</sup> <em data-effect="italics">M</em>, <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><msub><mtext>C</mtext><mn>6</mn></msub><msub><mtext>H</mtext><mn>4</mn></msub><msub><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mrow><mtext>CO</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><msup><mrow/><mrow><mn>2&#8722;</mn></mrow></msup><mo stretchy="false">]</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><msub><mtext>C</mtext><mn>6</mn></msub><msub><mtext>H</mtext><mn>4</mn></msub><msub><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mrow><mtext>CO</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><msup><mrow/><mrow><mn>2&#8722;</mn></mrow></msup><mo stretchy="false">]</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math>3.9 <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo>&#215;</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo>&#215;</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> 10<sup>&#8722;6</sup> <em data-effect="italics">M</em>, [OH<sup>&#8722;</sup>] 3.6 <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo>&#215;</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo>&#215;</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> 10<sup>&#8722;12</sup> <em data-effect="italics">M</em></p>
